<paragraph id="8BD436C28710AA0846A0F85CD846AB49" blockId="11.[189,1398,1919,2028]" lastBlockId="12.[189,1398,267,364]" lastPageId="12" lastPageNumber="13" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">
Cockerell considered describing 
<taxonomicName id="4C6B4D418710AA0F4420F85CD9D8ADE2" authorityName="Cockerell" authorityYear="1949" box="[573,696,1965,1992]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="robusta">
<emphasis id="B91FEAD08710AA0F4420F85CD9D8ADE2" box="[573,696,1965,1992]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">C. robusta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
under the name “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C6B4D418710AA0F459AF85CDF7DADE2" authorityName="Cockerell" authorityYear="1926" box="[903,1053,1965,1992]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="wilmattae">
<emphasis id="B91FEAD08710AA0F459AF85CDF7DADE2" box="[903,1053,1965,1992]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="12">C. wilmattae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
”, as an homage to his second wife. However, this name had already been used by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFFA4B338710AA0F4536F823DF60ADC9" author="Cockerell" box="[811,1024,2001,2028]" firstAuthor="Cockerell" pageId="11" pageNumber="12" pagination="214 - 226" refId="ref20022" refString="Cockerell, T. D. A. 1926 a. XXVIII. - Descriptions and records of bees. - CVIII. Annals and Magazine of Natural History 17 (98): 214 - 226. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00222932608633395" type="journal article" year="1926" yearSuffix="a">Cockerell (1926a)</bibRefCitation>
himself for a species described from 
<collectingRegion id="49AFF8208717AA0846E2FEF9DA0FAB00" box="[255,367,267,293]" country="Peru" name="Arequipa" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Arequipa</collectingRegion>
, southern 
<collectingCountry id="F37C76528717AA0847F2FEFED945AB03" box="[495,549,268,294]" name="Peru" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">Peru</collectingCountry>
(see below). 
<bibRefCitation id="EFFA4B338717AA0844D3FEFED815AB03" author="Moure" box="[718,885,267,294]" firstAuthor="Moure" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" pagination="114 - 123" refId="ref21409" refString="Moure J. S. 1969. Notas sobre algumas especies de Centris da Guiana (Hym., Apoidea). Anais da Academia brasileira de Ciencias 41 (1): 114 - 123." type="journal article" year="1969">Moure (1969)</bibRefCitation>
synonymized 
<taxonomicName id="4C6B4D418717AA084235FEFEDFC7AB00" authorityName="Cockerell" authorityYear="1949" box="[1064,1191,267,294]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="robusta">
<emphasis id="B91FEAD08717AA084235FEFEDFC7AB00" box="[1064,1191,267,294]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">C. robusta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
with 
<taxonomicName id="4C6B4D418717AA0842ECFEFEDE0FAB00" authorityName="Friese" authorityYear="1899" box="[1265,1391,268,294]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="12" pageNumber="13" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="inermis">
<emphasis id="B91FEAD08717AA0842ECFEFEDE0FAB00" box="[1265,1391,268,294]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="13">C. inermis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
